&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Ribamar FS - ribafs @ gmail.com&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Fortaleza, 27 de junho de 2017&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

