&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Vamos remover alguns itens para que fique assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Extensões - Temas&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Learnmate Free - Portal2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Mudando o Estilo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

