	<entry>
		<title>Adicionar Conteúdo</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://backup/portal/joomla-3/administracao/adicionar-conteudo.html"/>
		<published>2017-06-27T10:12:32-03:00</published>
		<updated>2017-06-27T10:12:32-03:00</updated>
		<id>http://backup/portal/joomla-3/administracao/adicionar-conteudo.html</id>
		<author>
			<name>Ribamar FS</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adicionar Conteúdo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Vamos adicionar a seguinte estrutura (categorias, artigos e itens de menu) de conteúdo ao site:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Criar as seguites categorias e subcategorias&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Laravel&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Joomla&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Main Menu&lt;br /&gt;Criar itens de menu para as categorias principais e para as subcategorias (subordinados aos principais), de forma que quando o mouse for movido sobre as categorias principais as subcategorias apareçam, como acontece aqui neste site (&lt;a href=&quot;http://backup/portal/../&quot; rel=&quot;alternate&quot;&gt;http://ribafs.org&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Meu de Topo&lt;br /&gt;    Contato&lt;br /&gt;    Sobre Mim   &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Mudar o item de menu existente no Main Manu de Home para Início, inclusive o apelido.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criando as Categorias Principais&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Conteúdo - Categorias - Criar Nova Categoria&lt;br /&gt;Título - CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Título - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Título - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criando as Subcategorias&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Conteúdo - Categorias - Criar Nova Categoria&lt;br /&gt;Título - Introdução&lt;br /&gt;Pai - CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo1.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Instalaçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Configuraçoes&lt;br /&gt;Pai - CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subcategorias da Laravel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Introduçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Instalaçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Configuraçoes&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subcategorias da Joomla&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Introduçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Instalaçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Configuraçoes&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Apos concluido ficara assim&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo2.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Nossas categorias e sub estao prontas para receber os artigos, mas antes vamos criar os itens de menu correspondentes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criar Itens de Menu do CakePHP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Menus - Main Menu - Adicionar Item de Menu&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Itens requeridos&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Titulo do Menu - CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Tipo de Item de Menu - clicar em Selecionar - Artigos - Lista de uma categoria&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Clicar em Selecionar (a direita de Lista de uma Categoria) e escolher CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Deve ficar assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo3.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; De forma semelhante criar as categorias Laravel e Joomla.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criar as SubCategorias&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Introduçao de CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Menus - Main Menu - Adicionar Item de Menu&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;A criaçao sera semelhante a da CakePHP, exceto que indicaremos uma categoria Pai, que neste casos era a CakePHP.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Titulo do Menu - Introduçao&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Tipo de Item de Menu - clicar em Selecionar - Artigos - Lista de uma categoria&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Clicar em Selecionar (a direita de Lista de uma Categoria) e escolher Introduçao (abaixo de CakePHP)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Deve ficar assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo4.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; De forma semelhante crie tambem os itens Instalaçao e Configuraçoes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Depois, de forma identica, crie as subs de Laravel e Joomla tambem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Veja como deve ficar ao final (os 3 tem os mesmos subitens).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo5.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; &lt;/p&gt;</summary>
		<content type="html">&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Adicionar Conteúdo&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Vamos adicionar a seguinte estrutura (categorias, artigos e itens de menu) de conteúdo ao site:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Criar as seguites categorias e subcategorias&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Laravel&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Joomla&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Main Menu&lt;br /&gt;Criar itens de menu para as categorias principais e para as subcategorias (subordinados aos principais), de forma que quando o mouse for movido sobre as categorias principais as subcategorias apareçam, como acontece aqui neste site (&lt;a href=&quot;http://backup/portal/../&quot; rel=&quot;alternate&quot;&gt;http://ribafs.org&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Meu de Topo&lt;br /&gt;    Contato&lt;br /&gt;    Sobre Mim   &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Mudar o item de menu existente no Main Manu de Home para Início, inclusive o apelido.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criando as Categorias Principais&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Conteúdo - Categorias - Criar Nova Categoria&lt;br /&gt;Título - CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Título - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Título - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criando as Subcategorias&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;    Introdução&lt;br /&gt;    Instalação&lt;br /&gt;    Configurações&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Conteúdo - Categorias - Criar Nova Categoria&lt;br /&gt;Título - Introdução&lt;br /&gt;Pai - CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo1.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Instalaçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Configuraçoes&lt;br /&gt;Pai - CakePHP&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subcategorias da Laravel&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Introduçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Instalaçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Configuraçoes&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Laravel&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Subcategorias da Joomla&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Introduçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Instalaçao&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Novo&lt;br /&gt;Titulo - Configuraçoes&lt;br /&gt;Pai - Joomla&lt;br /&gt;Salvar &amp;amp; Fechar&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Apos concluido ficara assim&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo2.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Nossas categorias e sub estao prontas para receber os artigos, mas antes vamos criar os itens de menu correspondentes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criar Itens de Menu do CakePHP&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Menus - Main Menu - Adicionar Item de Menu&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Itens requeridos&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Titulo do Menu - CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Tipo de Item de Menu - clicar em Selecionar - Artigos - Lista de uma categoria&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Clicar em Selecionar (a direita de Lista de uma Categoria) e escolher CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Deve ficar assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo3.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;br /&gt; &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; De forma semelhante criar as categorias Laravel e Joomla.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Criar as SubCategorias&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Introduçao de CakePHP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Menus - Main Menu - Adicionar Item de Menu&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;A criaçao sera semelhante a da CakePHP, exceto que indicaremos uma categoria Pai, que neste casos era a CakePHP.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Titulo do Menu - Introduçao&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Tipo de Item de Menu - clicar em Selecionar - Artigos - Lista de uma categoria&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Clicar em Selecionar (a direita de Lista de uma Categoria) e escolher Introduçao (abaixo de CakePHP)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Deve ficar assim:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://backup/portal/images/conteudo4.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt; De forma semelhante crie tambem os itens Instalaçao e Configuraçoes.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;Depois, de forma identica, crie as subs de Laravel e Joomla tambem.&lt;/p&gt;

